00:00.100 --> 00:02.160
Previously on "Switched at Birth"...

00:02.180 --> 00:05.034
- I'm still really angry at you.
- That's fine.

00:05.484 --> 00:07.496
You must go to school with Travis.

00:07.516 --> 00:10.122
- Yeah, I go to Carlton.
- You talk!

