00:16.977 --> 00:20.312
Wes: Two punks and this is the only frame
that shows any identifying features.

00:20.332 --> 00:23.073
It's from the entrance where they broke in,
but there's nothing from the site.

00:23.290 --> 00:27.148
How could you know and not tell me...
unless you were with him.

00:27.168 --> 00:30.186
She cost me hundreds of
thousands of dollars.

00:30.206 --> 00:33.490
- This is your project, too!
- I know.

00:33.510 --> 00:36.328
Wes, if our partnership means
anything to you,

00:36.348 --> 00:39.063
do not turn her in.

00:41.590 --> 00:43.975
You should go to USC,

00:43.995 --> 00:46.911
and I should come with you.

00:51.704 --> 00:53.561
- Hey.
- Hey.

00:53.581 --> 00:56.273
So I have been giving a lot of thought

00:56.293 --> 00:59.039
to what I want to do after graduation.

00:59.209 --> 01:00.896
I want to move to L.A. with Emmett.

01:00.916 --> 01:02.798
Move to California?

01:02.832 --> 01:05.768
Uh, let me see. That would be a "no."

01:05.802 --> 01:08.837
I'm trying to have an adult
discussion about this.

01:08.872 --> 01:12.775
Following your boyfriend across the country
like a puppy dog is not an adult move.

01:12.809 --> 01:15.644
- Dad!
- Emmett is gonna be busy with school.

01:15.678 --> 01:18.639
- What will you be doing?
- I'm not sure yet,

01:18.659 --> 01:21.290
- but I'll probably hang with Emmett...
- In his dorm.

01:21.310 --> 01:24.620
Just until I get the lay of the land,
and I'll get a job right away.

01:24.654 --> 01:28.224
And I've already started looking
at art schools. I'll figure it out.

01:28.244 --> 01:30.592
I think it's pretty clear that
you haven't figured it out.

01:30.627 --> 01:32.050
Yes, I have.

01:32.070 --> 01:34.785
Really? So what about your airplane ticket?

01:34.805 --> 01:37.974
And where are you gonna live after
Emmett's R.A. kicks you out of his dorm?

01:37.994 --> 01:40.202
And what about a car to get
around that big old town in?

01:40.236 --> 01:43.907
And how in God's name are
you going to pay for it all?

01:43.927 --> 01:45.407
Well,
I don't know what you guys were planning

01:45.442 --> 01:47.176
on doing for my graduation gift.

01:47.210 --> 01:48.786
Don't even finish that sentence.

01:48.806 --> 01:50.112
For us to even consider this,

01:50.146 --> 01:53.042
you have to come up with
a very realistic plan.

01:53.062 --> 01:56.405
So you're saying if I come
up with a realistic plan,

01:56.425 --> 01:59.188
- I can go?
- Sure.

01:59.798 --> 02:01.498
- Fine.
- Fine.

02:03.596 --> 02:05.805
