02:09.900 --> 02:12.456
Okay, remember,
everyone has to sign for their yearbook,

02:12.476 --> 02:16.018
and you don't get yours if you
still have textbooks to turn in.

02:16.038 --> 02:19.393
I think, like, 0% of this class is
paying attention to you right now.

02:19.413 --> 02:20.876
Yeah, it's seniors on their last day.

02:20.910 --> 02:23.933
I might as well be herding cats.
There we go.

02:23.953 --> 02:25.182
