You're back.

03:30.613 --> 03:33.615
Hi. How was Hawaii?

03:33.649 --> 03:35.043
The Mahi Mahi, the Mai Tais,

03:35.063 --> 03:36.308
the view from the balcony,

03:36.328 --> 03:37.959
it was all fantastic.

03:37.979 --> 03:39.882
Business wasn't bad either.

03:40.180 --> 03:42.208
I can't wait to hear all about it.

03:42.228 --> 03:43.425
Yes, you can.

03:43.459 --> 03:44.626
Excuse me.

03:44.660 --> 03:47.095
Well, I can smell polite shop talk
from a mile away.

03:47.115 --> 03:48.797
What you really want to know is

03:48.831 --> 03:50.731
what I'm gonna do about Daphne.

03:52.802 --> 03:54.703
I've been worried sick.

03:54.737 --> 03:58.673
Look,
I'm sorry I got so upset before I left.

03:58.999 --> 04:02.006
But being away was good,
allowed me to clear my head

04:02.026 --> 04:03.345
and think about things.

04:03.379 --> 04:04.679
And?

04:05.814 --> 04:07.712
No one will ever know she was involved.

04:07.732 --> 04:09.338
(Sighs)

04:09.996 --> 04:13.288
Thank you. Thank you. Thank you.

04:15.543 --> 04:17.743
I love Hawaii Wes.

04:29.733 --> 04:31.296
Wait.

04:31.569 --> 04:33.508
I... I can't.

04:36.533 --> 04:39.627
- I'm sorry.
- It's just...

04:40.247 --> 04:41.483
too soon.

04:41.517 --> 04:43.623
Right, of course.

04:44.665 --> 04:46.055
Wait.

04:46.911 --> 04:47.722
That wasn't...

04:47.757 --> 04:51.155
you don't think that because you're
doing something for Daphne that I...

04:51.175 --> 04:53.310
What? No! No, God. No.

04:53.330 --> 04:56.126
- This wasn't some kind of...
- Good.

04:56.732 --> 05:00.136
I'm sorry. I just wanna keep this...

05:00.156 --> 05:02.537
Professional. Right, right.

05:02.750 --> 05:04.239
I got it.

05:04.698 --> 05:06.262
Professional.

05:09.336 --> 05:11.963
Hey, those are so cool.

05:11.983 --> 05:15.140
_

