07:28.695 --> 07:30.099
My dad wasn't kidding.

07:30.119 --> 07:33.465
Apartments in L.A. are expensive.

07:33.925 --> 07:37.437
I found this small artist's loft.
It's near downtown.

07:37.457 --> 07:39.943
It's ten minutes from USC.

07:39.963 --> 07:41.896
They need first and last,

07:41.931 --> 07:43.598
plus a security deposit.

07:43.632 --> 07:46.091
That and my airfare,

07:46.111 --> 07:48.761
it's almost $5,000.

07:49.431 --> 07:50.839
I'm going to need a job right away.

07:50.873 --> 07:54.189
Oh! Maybe we could drive
the thing out there

07:54.209 --> 07:56.167
to save on a plane ticket.

07:56.187 --> 07:59.815
_

