20:18.287 --> 20:20.829
I've ruined my whole life.

20:21.092 --> 20:22.396
Don't say that.

20:22.416 --> 20:24.032
No, look, I know that

20:24.067 --> 20:27.069
it seems bad right now,

20:27.103 --> 20:29.201
but it is only three months.

20:29.221 --> 20:32.007
And when you get out,
you'll get back on track.

20:32.041 --> 20:34.643
You will go to Gallaudet
and then med school.

20:34.677 --> 20:36.051
Med school?

20:36.071 --> 20:38.930
I will be a convicted felon.

20:38.950 --> 20:42.971
Convicted felons don't go to med school.
That's over.

20:45.067 --> 20:46.888
I had no idea.

20:48.725 --> 20:51.036
All my plans,

20:51.056 --> 20:54.525
everything that I worked so hard for,

20:55.171 --> 20:58.600
will be gone the minute I
walk into that police station.

