21:06.068 --> 21:08.510
- We have to go in.
- I can't do it.

21:09.133 --> 21:12.935
I can't stand up there
and give this speech.

21:12.955 --> 21:14.842
I can't.

21:22.909 --> 21:25.763
You can do this. Come on.

