22:07.019 --> 22:09.331
I would like to welcome everyone

22:09.351 --> 22:14.506
to the 2014 Carlton School graduation.

22:21.157 --> 22:25.128
It is with great pleasure and pride

22:25.148 --> 22:29.063
that I welcome our student speaker.

22:29.083 --> 22:32.153
She was been voted overwhelmingly

22:32.173 --> 22:35.578
by her class to represent them today.

22:35.598 --> 22:38.345
A young woman I have known

22:38.365 --> 22:41.138
for more than a decade,

22:41.158 --> 22:44.377
Ms. Daphne Vasquez.

23:18.454 --> 23:21.284
Good afternoon, parents,

23:21.304 --> 23:24.663
siblings, teachers,

23:24.697 --> 23:26.898
and my fellow graduates.

23:29.635 --> 23:31.958
Until I was eight years old,

23:31.978 --> 23:34.788
I went to a hearing school.

23:34.808 --> 23:37.990
There I struggled

23:38.325 --> 23:40.049
to read lips,

23:40.069 --> 23:42.714
to follow what was happening around me.

23:44.574 --> 23:48.049
Struggled to make friends.

23:48.632 --> 23:52.640
Nobody liked to sit next to the weird,
deaf girl.

23:53.725 --> 23:56.951
But I was incredibly lucky.

23:56.971 --> 24:00.749
Because one day, an eight year old boy

24:00.769 --> 24:05.376
walking by my playground
on his way home saw me.

24:06.232 --> 24:08.408
He took me by the hand

24:08.428 --> 24:11.772
and led me back to his house.

24:12.445 --> 24:15.755
Introduced me to his mom.

24:17.158 --> 24:20.118
Introduced me to sign language.

24:21.196 --> 24:24.256
Introduced me to Carlton.

24:25.738 --> 24:28.679
And I've been here ever since.

24:29.436 --> 24:32.544
When they threatened to
close down our school,

24:32.564 --> 24:35.461
we fought valiantly

24:35.481 --> 24:38.439
for something that we truly believed in...

24:38.459 --> 24:40.176
deaf education.

24:40.196 --> 24:43.875
While Carlton didn't stay fully deaf,

24:43.910 --> 24:46.489
it did stay open

24:46.613 --> 24:49.753
one more year so that we all

24:49.754 --> 24:53.010
could graduate together today,

24:53.030 --> 24:56.696
and for that, I am so thankful

24:57.118 --> 24:59.128
and so proud.

24:59.492 --> 25:02.520
I'll admit that like many of us,

25:02.540 --> 25:05.473
I was nervous about hearing students

25:05.493 --> 25:08.433
invading our campus,

25:08.861 --> 25:12.059
but I was wrong to be nervous.

25:13.027 --> 25:15.099
The truth is

25:15.844 --> 25:19.256
one of those hearing "invaders"

25:19.976 --> 25:22.380
became one of the best friends

25:22.415 --> 25:24.416
that I've ever had.

25:26.563 --> 25:30.497
We weren't able to save
our school this time.

25:30.517 --> 25:32.991
(Booing)

25:33.951 --> 25:37.363
But we graduate today the final class

25:37.383 --> 25:38.976
of Carlton...

25:38.996 --> 25:42.475
diverse, unified,

25:42.495 --> 25:44.746
and most of all

25:45.453 --> 25:49.499
optimistic about our future.

25:52.179 --> 25:53.767
(Sighs)

25:53.980 --> 25:57.242
The last thing I'd like
to say today is thank you.

25:58.446 --> 26:01.536
A huge thank you to all of our families,

26:01.556 --> 26:04.790
but especially our siblings.

26:09.154 --> 26:11.425
No matter how we got them.

26:13.349 --> 26:15.788
And to our parents.

26:17.437 --> 26:21.633
Who have been there for us,
through everything.

