32:00.811 --> 32:02.591
And here come the waterworks.

32:02.626 --> 32:06.495
I can't believe it. My God. Look at you.

32:08.350 --> 32:11.626
My baby graduating from high school.

32:11.646 --> 32:15.213
You are such an incredible
talented young woman.

32:15.560 --> 32:18.428
I thought you were upset
at me for moving to L.A.?

32:18.448 --> 32:21.277
Well, I am a bit nervous.

32:21.311 --> 32:23.012
But you're right.

32:23.046 --> 32:25.931
You're old enough to make up your own mind.

32:26.501 --> 32:28.827
- Hi.
- Hey.

32:44.474 --> 32:45.939
(Sniffling)

32:50.136 --> 32:52.605
Okay, enough tears.

32:57.023 --> 32:59.838
How's it going, high school graduate?

33:00.645 --> 33:02.270
Back atcha.

33:02.531 --> 33:06.489
Hey,
so kick some ass at St. Louis U. next year.

33:06.509 --> 33:09.282
Will do. You do the same at Gallaudet.

33:17.069 --> 33:19.295
- Hey.
- Hey, lady.

33:19.315 --> 33:20.411
So I'm gonna go.

33:20.431 --> 33:23.345
But I'll see you guys at grad night, right?

33:23.365 --> 33:25.623
- Totally.
- Okay, see you.

33:29.669 --> 33:34.462
You promised that we would
have one more normal day.

33:34.482 --> 33:37.353
I can't. I can't go off to some party

33:37.387 --> 33:41.270
and pretend like my whole life
isn't over in a few hours.

33:42.481 --> 33:44.074
I'm gonna sneak out of here

33:44.094 --> 33:47.122
and go to the police
station and turn myself in.

33:49.021 --> 33:51.714
Have fun for both of us.

34:13.004 --> 34:15.958
Okay, I'm coming with you.

34:15.992 --> 34:17.993
What? No, I don't want you to miss the...

34:18.027 --> 34:20.524
You're not doing this alone.

34:25.588 --> 34:26.835
Let's go.

34:28.963 --> 34:30.960
- (Sighs)
- (Engine turns over)

34:34.141 --> 34:37.676
- I'm here about the noise.
- What noise?

34:37.710 --> 34:40.123
There isn't any. It's too quiet.

34:41.686 --> 34:45.016
Are you okay?
You seemed a little down today.

34:45.051 --> 34:48.333
Yeah, I just have a few things on my mind.

34:48.353 --> 34:50.938
Anything you want to talk about?

34:51.647 --> 34:54.630
My ex-wife left me a message today.

34:55.003 --> 34:57.721
She wants an annulment.

34:57.741 --> 34:59.247
Why?

34:59.267 --> 35:02.629
Clean slate in the eyes of the church,
I guess.

35:03.089 --> 35:05.062
Nikki's pretty religious.

35:10.613 --> 35:13.512
This doesn't mean that
she's forgotten about you

35:13.547 --> 35:15.414
or that it didn't mean anything

35:15.449 --> 35:18.171
- or even that she isn't still hurting.
- I know.

35:18.191 --> 35:20.565
I've been saying the same things to myself

35:20.585 --> 35:23.289
for the last two hours.

35:24.635 --> 35:26.000
Thank you.

35:26.326 --> 35:29.053
You have your music and your family

35:29.073 --> 35:31.163
and a million friends.

35:31.198 --> 35:34.003
I do. I do.

35:34.859 --> 35:36.981
The thing is...

35:37.001 --> 35:39.947
there's a million people

35:39.967 --> 35:42.065
to do something with,

35:42.085 --> 35:45.701
but there's just nobody

35:45.721 --> 35:48.195
to do nothing with.

35:49.585 --> 35:53.252
That's what I miss the most.

35:59.001 --> 36:01.026
I better...

36:03.690 --> 36:07.847
actually,
I was thinking about going upstairs

36:08.405 --> 36:10.317
and doing nothing.

36:11.830 --> 36:13.806
Do you want to come?

36:14.534 --> 36:18.210
Yeah, I'd love that.

36:24.566 --> 36:28.821
I know it wasn't you who
pressed charges against her.

36:29.728 --> 36:31.118
Who was it?

36:31.242 --> 36:33.270
The owner of the construction site.

36:33.290 --> 36:34.727
I spoke to my attorney.

36:34.761 --> 36:37.696
- I'm sorry. I shouldn't have...
- It's okay.

36:38.335 --> 36:40.052
Been a hell of a year.

36:40.072 --> 36:41.634
I know.

36:43.001 --> 36:45.302
I pulled out of East Riverside.

36:45.322 --> 36:47.313
No. No, no, no.

36:47.333 --> 36:51.296
It wasn't you or your daughter,
any of this.

36:52.214 --> 36:54.786
It was just everything.

36:54.806 --> 36:56.896
Wasn't meant to be.

37:09.350 --> 37:11.764
Come with me to Hawaii.

37:13.371 --> 37:14.265
What?

37:14.285 --> 37:15.925
Well, your girls are out of the house.

37:15.945 --> 37:18.370
You need something new, a fresh start.

37:18.405 --> 37:20.439
Plus it's Hawaii.

37:21.435 --> 37:23.296
And...

37:23.991 --> 37:26.545
- I need you.
- Wes.

37:26.733 --> 37:29.895
I'll get you your own place
so there's no pressure.

37:30.230 --> 37:34.186
It'll be great to work on
something without any angry locals.

37:34.220 --> 37:37.456
Wes, with everything that's
going on with Daphne.

37:37.753 --> 37:41.116
I know. It's bad timing.

37:41.361 --> 37:44.363
But what are you gonna do,
just sit around and be miserable?

37:44.715 --> 37:47.644
Don't you deserve your own life?

37:48.589 --> 37:51.370
Please just say "yes."

37:52.597 --> 37:54.273
Please.

37:59.357 --> 38:01.082
John.

38:05.450 --> 38:07.378
How did this happen?

38:08.979 --> 38:10.189
How?

38:10.223 --> 38:12.292
Oh, sweetheart.

38:12.312 --> 38:14.938
I mean, it feels like we just got her.

38:16.650 --> 38:18.864
She's just a kid.

38:19.132 --> 38:21.664
She's not a kid anymore.

38:21.974 --> 38:24.061
I think we're gonna have
to try to accept that.

38:24.081 --> 38:27.524
I just cannot believe that I can't
do anything more to help her.

38:27.544 --> 38:30.427
There's nothing anybody can do.

38:30.447 --> 38:33.078
What is going to happen to her?

38:33.592 --> 38:36.514
I'll tell you what's
going to happen to her.

38:36.534 --> 38:39.157
She's gonna live through this.

38:39.177 --> 38:41.142
And so are we.

38:49.829 --> 38:53.396
Does your attorney know that you're here?
I can call her.

38:56.451 --> 38:58.970
I just want to get this over with.

38:58.990 --> 39:00.869
You're entitled to an interpreter. I can...

39:00.889 --> 39:02.743
No, I'm fine.

39:03.227 --> 39:05.063
All right, go ahead.

39:07.228 --> 39:09.040
A couple of weeks ago...

39:09.060 --> 39:12.484
I vandalized the construction site.

39:14.500 --> 39:16.163
Excuse me.

39:16.790 --> 39:19.385
It was me, not her.

39:19.820 --> 39:24.878
You found Daphne's fingerprints on the
tractor because she was there to stop me.

39:24.898 --> 39:27.461
- But I wouldn't listen.
- Bay.

39:27.481 --> 39:30.323
Don't try to take the blame anymore.

39:30.343 --> 39:32.593
I can't watch you do that.

39:32.613 --> 39:33.810
Bay what...?

39:33.946 --> 39:34.496
_

39:36.292 --> 39:38.352
