39:38.678 --> 39:40.144
What's going on?

39:40.164 --> 39:43.564
It was my biological father who died,
not hers.

39:43.584 --> 39:45.632
She barely knew him.

39:45.652 --> 39:47.989
I was angry at my mom.

39:48.009 --> 39:50.756
They got into a big fight before he died

39:50.790 --> 39:52.370
and I wanted to get back at her.

39:52.390 --> 39:53.400
Hold on a second.

39:53.420 --> 39:57.696
And the the black spray paint that
was used at the site, that's mine.

39:57.731 --> 39:59.597
I have a bunch of it in
my art studio at home.

39:59.617 --> 40:01.980
I've been doing street
art for a long time now.

40:02.000 --> 40:05.504
I can show you some of the places
that I've tagged around town.

40:06.013 --> 40:08.674
All right, stay right here.

40:08.694 --> 40:10.767
Don't move.

